Get in touch
Miranda Cuisine & Bar is less than than 15 minutes away from major city centers around Miami-Dade, and is on 3 main city corridors.(NW 36th street, LeJeune Rd, and State 112), making the venue an ideal meeting place for friends, family or business meetings.
If you have questions or comments, please get a hold of us in whichever way is most convenient. Ask away. There is no reasonable question that our team can not answer.
If you are interested in joining Miranda Cuisine & Bar, please send your contact information, the position you will be applying to, and a phone number we can reach to you. We’re always evaluating individuals to be part of our team in the various positions such as: servers, bus-person, line cooks, food preps, sous chef, bartenders.
